{"tid":1265794,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲香港留學生唔好再向外國人介紹自己係Chinese!!!","createTime":"2019-06-29T11:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T11:55:32.000Z","uid":248275,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f93c43846b58b776a304d161f8ca7618490aefdc","tid":1265794,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"識好多外國留學嘅朋友會直接以「I&rsquo;m Chinese」介紹自己<br />\n希望你地以後會以Hong Kongese或者Hongkonger自稱<br />\n<br />\n呢次抗爭香港對國際發放左一大信念「香港不是中國」、「香港正抗衡中國」<br />\n而呢樣亦係我地要維護，甚至繼續宣揚國際嘅信念<br />\n<br />\n可能你地為左方便或者唔會得罪內地留學生而用「chinese」自稱<br />\n但希望你地可以為左香港長遠嘅地位同利益，同喺香港生活緊同香港人結連，自稱香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8048d9b225bfbc1d222ad13e668a6952fc4f0f","tid":1265794,"uid":176081,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"從來都無稱過自己做chinese 同埋不停同人講 香港唔撚係中國"},{"pid":"f52e4264206ddc49a6361856325962404cbe128b","tid":1265794,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"2f8048d9b225bfbc1d222ad13e668a6952fc4f0f","tid":1265794,"uid":176081,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"從來都無稱過自己做chinese 同埋不停同人講 香港唔撚係中國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我啲美國frd全撚部係講I&rsquo;m chinese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c3787b1e05f24da13089fa79658fe29dab1e3e","tid":1265794,"uid":213048,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:24:15.000Z","msg":"第一日識朋友都已經係<br />\nI'm from Hong Kong."},{"pid":"c7c0c8d56ce38760d81d07f05f3c60eda42ce170","tid":1265794,"uid":248275,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"好多人都冇連登仔咁醒<br />\n或者留左幾年嘅都係自稱chinese<br />\n<br />\n同埋「I&rsquo;m hong kongese」會比「I&rsquo;m from hong kong」更直接宣認香港人嘅身分<br />\n好似有人會以城市介紹自己講「I&rsquo;m from new york」「I&rsquo;m from shanghai」咁"},{"pid":"a889e5fa370465d0ae57b6cb3ccd5d2bbc372cfe","tid":1265794,"uid":96146,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:34:10.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係講from hong kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7026542dc8c260f472fd616e5aae61ac97afc5e7","tid":1265794,"uid":271130,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"去過外國留學既都知 從來冇香港人會介紹自己係Chinese <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而以前見過好多廣東既同學仔 同鬼佬講自己from Hong Kong <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc125403ef0ef684d1567c00b6499e69d0091c9","tid":1265794,"uid":132896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"今日係日本食野<br />\n個老板娘想同我地傾計<br />\n問China?<br />\n我即刻話糾正話係香港<br />\n然後話China 唔好個啲"},{"pid":"e7dc19f14b49101b75c4502e314d1cc75e1434e2","tid":1265794,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7026542dc8c260f472fd616e5aae61ac97afc5e7","tid":1265794,"uid":271130,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"去過外國留學既都知 從來冇香港人會介紹自己係Chinese <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而以前見過好多廣東既同學仔 同鬼佬講自己from Hong Kong <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"事關反送中果排有文宣係我美國朋友果邊<br />\n然後張poster係China果個位有個交叉<br />\n然後啲人話咁樣唔appropriate，因為佢地平時同人講自己係chinese但又交叉左個China，然後就唔肯spread果張圖，我都係之後同啲frd傾返先知好多都仲係直接話自己Chinese<br />\n如果叫開hong kongese嘅當然好，但如果識其他香港留學生可以幫手呼籲下"},{"pid":"4745ea01aaaaf429c18f35c6fb0e5793294fa55d","tid":1265794,"uid":124507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"I am not a fxxking Chinese! I am hongkongness/konger"},{"pid":"11bcdaf30451762a0cc7cbe7dd24d8ee185b8735","tid":1265794,"uid":33004,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"